    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "The `or` operator returns `True` if at least one of the conditions evalute to `True`. It returns `False` only if both conditions are `False`.¥n",
        "¥n",
        "| `a`     | `b`    | `a or b`  |¥n",
        "|---------|--------|-----------|¥n",
        "|  `True` | `True` | `True`    |¥n",
        "|  `True` | `False`| `True`    |¥n",
        "|  `False`| `True` | `True`    |¥n",
        "|  `False`| `False`| `False`   |¥n"
